Name: OCS Consulting (Netherlands)
Description: OCS Consulting is a market leader in SAS consulting in the Netherlands. Since 1998, we support our clients with specialised services for data science, business intelligence, (bio) statistics and statistical programming. Often, OCS Consulting is also responsible for the installation and maintenance of the SAS environments. For the BeNeLux, DACH, French, Spanish and UK markets, OCS Consulting is also a SAS Reseller Partner for all official SAS software licenses, including LSAF® and JMP®. In 2021, OCS Consulting was named the SAS Local Partner of the Year for Southwest Europe. As such, we have unique credentials to deliver all necessary services to get the best results out of your SAS platform. In October 2016 we achieved the SAS Gold-partner status and in the same year OCS Consulting won the SAS Reseller Partner of the Year Award. We continuously invest in the quality, knowledge and expertise of our consultants. With over 80 SAS certificates in 15 different disciplines, OCS Consulting holds all three competency badges for data management, visualisation and analytics, offered by SAS. In summary: our clients can count on our professionalism and expertise
